= SDL_LowerBlit =
Use this function to perform low-level surface blitting only.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_LowerBlit(SDL_Surface* src,
                  SDL_Rect*    srcrect,
                  SDL_Surface* dst,
                  SDL_Rect*    dstrect)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''src'''
|a pointer to the [[SDL_Surface]] containing '''srcrect'''
|-
|'''srcrect'''
|a pointer to the source [[SDL_Rect]] to be queried
|-
|'''dst'''
|a pointer to the destination [[SDL_Surface]] containing '''dstrect'''
|-
|'''dstrect'''
|a pointer to the destination [[SDL_Rect]] to be filled
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns 0 on success or a negative error code on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

